      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "その時は、ひまわり畑だけじゃなくて\n怜も一緒に写真に写るのはどうだ？",
      "startTime": 227.2333262126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ひまわりの花は怜によく似合っているから\n写真映えもするだろうしな",
      "startTime": 232.9666595459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
